At Bookmates Inc., we respect our users' privacy and understand that they may want to delete their account at some point. To ensure that this process is carried out smoothly and securely, we have established a "Delete Account" policy.

To request the deletion of your account, please send an email to theortran@gmail.com with the subject line "Account Deletion Request". In the email, please include your full name and the email address associated with your account.

Please note that the deletion process may take up to 10 business days to complete. Once your account has been deleted, all of your personal information and data will be permanently removed from our system and cannot be recovered.

We may retain certain information related to your account for legal and administrative purposes, such as records of transactions or communications with our customer support team.

Thank you for choosing Bookmates Inc., and we hope to serve you again in the future.
